data.description:
Incredible opportunity to ASSUME sellers' current  loan with a RATE OF 2.99%!!  Welcome to Wyndwater, where the Azalea floor plan awaits--a haven for those who cherish the art of entertainment and luxurious living. This 4-bedroom, 3 1/2-bathroom residence is a masterpiece of design, offering a spacious and airy open-concept layout that defines modern coastal living.The heart of this home is the stunning kitchen, a chef's dream equipped with upgraded stainless-steel appliances, quartz countertops, a captivating tile backsplash, and an expansive island that doubles as a culinary masterpiece and a gathering place for friends and family.  As a testament to modern living, the Samsung oven performs culinary wonders--from bread-proofing to dehydrating, air frying, and warming. The Samsung Refrigerator with Smart Hub adds a touch of technological sophistication to the heart of the home. With over 20 feet of countertops, the kitchen becomes a workspace and a statement of contemporary design.Discover convenience at every turn with a thoughtfully designed mudroom featuring built-ins, ensuring a clutter-free entryway. Large telescoping glass doors seamlessly connect the kitchen to a screened-in outdoor patio, extending your living space to a generously sized and fenced-in backyard adorned with Zoysia grass and an efficient irrigation system.Tray ceilings and a gas fireplace grace the large family room, creating an inviting ambiance that beckons for shared moments and cozy gatherings.  Further, indulge in the finer details that elevate this home to a level of sophistication. Coffered ceilings, crown molding, and wainscoting add a touch of timeless elegance, complemented by the luxury vinyl plank flooring that exudes both style and practicality. Recessed lighting throughout enhances the architectural features, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Ascend to the second level, where the master bedroom awaits with an expansive walk-in closet, providing a private retreat for relaxation. The sizable laundry room, equipped for efficiency, is centrally located along with three additional bedrooms down the hall.
This prime location places you just minutes away from the area's pristine beaches, shopping, parks, and restaurants, ensuring that every convenience is within reach. Live the coastal lifestyle you've dreamed of in this meticulously designed Azalea floor plana home where entertainment meets elegance, and every detail is a testament to refined living.
